An Invitation to Dine
Midnight Supper
Appetizer
Fresh cracked Snow Crab claw, with cocktail sauce, stuffed tomato with baby shrimp salad.
stuffed egg, aged Gouda cheese, California artichoke hearts, slice of sirloin roast with a variety of garnishes
Salad
Waldorf Salad, a mixture of finely sliced hearts of celery, black raisins and Washington apples blended with
sour cream and mayonnaise, seasoned lightly and garnished with walnuts and fresh orange slices
For Your Entree Choice
HOT DELI SANDWICH
Specialty sandwich, either a lean hot pastrami and corned beef on rye or
a grilled Reuben with corned beef, aged Swiss cheese and sauerkraut
(Ask Flight Attendant for today's selection)
— or —
QUICHE LORRAINE
An egg mixture with aged cheese, onion, and ham, in a light pastry crust
herb stuffed broiled tomato
- or —
CHEESE BLINTZES
with sour cream and hot blueberry sauce
For Dessert
ORANGE SURPRISE
Delightfully light orange sherbet in a sculptured orange shell, topped with Maraschino cherry
Assorted cheese and fruits
Fortune and sesame cookies
Prior to arrival, we invite you to enjoy orange juice and a variety of hot buttered Danish
Please accept our apology if, due to previous passenger selections, your choice is not available.
